Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.model.interfaces

Interface ContentMetadataInterface.ContentNodeMetadata

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<ContentMetadataInterface.ContentNodeMetadata>
All Known Implementing Classes:
MutableContentNodeMetadata
Enclosing interface:
ContentMetadataInterface
public static interface ContentMetadataInterface.ContentNodeMetadata
extends java.lang.Iterable<ContentMetadataInterface.ContentNodeMetadata>

This interface describes a node in the model tree. This node implements Iterable interface to get access for all children with for-each loop

Since:
0.0.3
Author:
